title: Looking for Mid, Jungle, Top and Support for ranked 5's
body:
Hey, I wanted to make I somewhat serious team. I'm looking for players who want to practice, and to learn together as a team, and willing to play a decent amount of games per day (3 to 5). 

Requirements:
1.) HAVE FUN
2.) Don't be toxic
3.) Must be mature.
4.) Try to make our set practice times. (TBD)
5.) Be Gold 1+
6.) have TS3.

http://www.teamspeak.com/?page=downloads
